<P>
   SCI-HERB-CANCER (Undated) _ A Chinese herb used for weight loss,
aristoloquia fangxi, has been linked to bladder cancer, researchers
reported. By Denise Grady.
</P>
<P>
   SCI-ABORTION-PILL (Washington) _ On the abortion pill Ru486,
whose approval for use in the United States has been stalled. By
Sheryl Gay Stolberg. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   DKNY-WORKERS-LAWSUIT (New York) _ A class action suit was filed
against the Donna Karan Co., accusing the fashion company of
running a sweat shop and paying immigrant workers less than minimum
wage. By John Sullivan.
