<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-07 13:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6999 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-OLY-SYDNEY-BOS &LR;      06-07 1514
