<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-07 13:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7020 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-ELDERS-EDUCATE-ART-BO     06-07 1120
