   MICROSOFT _ WASHINGTON _ U.S. District Judge Thomas Penfield
Jackson issues a ruling at 3 p.m. EDT in the Microsoft antitrust
case that is expected to break the software giant into two parts.
Details of the historic ruling, its significance, and what's next
in the legal process. (Glass, Cox News Service).
