</P>
<P>
   CANCER-EXPERIMENT (Undated) _ An Arizona couple thwarted in
their bid to have their son's cancer treated by controversial
Houston doctor Stanislaw Burzynski have taken the boy to Mexico for
the same alternative therapy tried by basketball player Kim Perrot
a year ago. The boy, Thomas Navarro, is receiving insulin-induced
coma treatment, an experimental therapy that is showing promise in
advanced cancer patients but had not previously been studied in
humans or animals. By TODD ACKERMAN.
</P>
