 &HT;    _Save money and repair tears in large screen enclosure _ easily
(comes with illustration).
 &HT;    _Various tips for clearing up very old oil stains in garage.
 &HT;    _Getting rid of moss proliferating on roof top: a simple
household product and lots of water.
 &HT;    _How to measure up and cut hardwood boards of inexact widths.
