<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-07 16:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7239 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r l BC-INTERNET-POPCULTURE-T     06-07 0885
