<P>
   HKN-CUP-GAME5 (East Rutherford, N.J.) _ It's simple really. For
the New Jersey Devils and Dallas Stars, this game comes down to one
premise: If the Devils win, they capture the Stanley Cup for the
second time in six years. The defending champion Stars have no
choice but victory or they go home for the summer. By Nancy
