<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 
The Arizona Republic plans to move the following stories for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for Thursday, June 8. If you
have any questions, please call the Republic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
MONTINI-COLUMN (Phoenix) - ``Fetch!'' Sheriff Joe Arpaio said,
earlier this week, and we did. We obey Arpaio's command to sit at
press conferences. We beg for quotes. Roll over. And, when the
sheriff finally rears back and tosses a craggy rod of information
out into the desert, we hurl ourselves after it, the whole pack of
us, gnawing on the stick and howling loud enough for everyone in
the whole nation to hear. By E.J. MONTINI. Story will move in the
``A'' and ``K'' categories. &QL; 
